# The devcontainer build context is the repo root, but the Dockerfile only
# COPYs .devcontainer/.zshrc — everything else is wasted transfer to the
# daemon. The workspace is bind-mounted at runtime, never baked into the image.
# Exclude the heavy, regenerable trees (the repo is multi-GB without this).
.git
node_modules
**/node_modules
target
**/target
**/dist
**/.next
**/build
.claude/worktrees
**/*.log
